<p>ã“ã“ã§</p>

\[\mathcal{U}_{\rho \sigma} 
\equiv \mathcal{T}_{\rho \sigma} + \eta_{\rho \sigma} \mathcal{S} \tag{17}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®\(\mathcal{U}_{\rho \sigma}\)ã®\(00, 0i, ij\)æˆåˆ†ã‚’ã€ãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ¬ãƒ³ãƒ„ã‚²ãƒ¼ã‚¸(\(\bar{h}_{\mu \nu}^{\ \ \ \ \ ,\nu} = 0\))ã¨TTã‚²ãƒ¼ã‚¸(\(\bar{h} = 0\))ã‚’èª²ã—ã¦è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[\begin{align}
\mathcal{U}_{00} 
&amp;= \mathcal{T}_{00} + \eta_{00} \mathcal{S} 
= \frac{1}{2\kappa} (\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) + \frac{1}{4\kappa} (\partial^\rho \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) (\partial_\rho \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) \notag \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{2\kappa} (\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) + \frac{1}{4\kappa} (\eta^{\rho \alpha} \partial_\alpha \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) (\partial_\rho \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) \notag \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{2\kappa} (\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) + \frac{1}{4\kappa} (- \partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) + \frac{1}{4\kappa} (\partial_i \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) (\partial_i \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) \notag \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{4\kappa} \{(\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) + (\partial_i \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) (\partial_i \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) \} \tag{18}
