= - (\partial_0 \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_0 \bar{h}^{\mu \nu}) + (\partial_i \bar{h}_{\mu \nu}) (\partial_i \bar{h}^{\mu \nu})
= 0 \notag \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \ 
